      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为时间线从1到4共四个阶段，Created v1和Updated v2作为基础版本先出现。但Security_IntrusionDetection和Security_ZeroTrust的层级关系我有点不确定——IntrusionDetection是附着在\"System Created\"事件上，而ZeroTrust是\"System Updated\"？",
